        "subject": "LU-5559 ptlrpc: Keep reverse imports upon reconnections",
        "message": "LU-5559 ptlrpc: Keep reverse imports upon reconnections\n\nIf a client reconnects with the same handle as the one the server\nalready has, there seems to be no reason for the server to recreate a\nnew reverse import.  Keeping the existing one allows any in-flight\nASTs to be resent.\n\nChange-Id: Ic5df84242c4ecf21b6228ca482f70b0a2f4a80fa\nSigned-off-by: Li Wei <wei.g.li@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
